arking:</h2><p>The main car park next to the studio has free parking for 3 hours, Monday to Saturday, no restrictions after 6.00pm and on Sundays.*</p><h2>Getting there:</h2><ul><li>from Aylesbury - Take the A418 Stone Road out of Aylesbury, drive to the main roundabout outside Thame (by the Esso petrol station), take the second exit which goes to the town centre, bearing left at the first mini-roundabout which takes you on to North Street, left again at the second mini roundabout and you are on the Upper High Street. 20 minutes</li><li>from Oxford – Take the Headington route out of Oxford, or the Headington exit from the ring road; take the A40 southbound, after Wheatley take the A418 towards Thame/Aylesbury, continue on the A418 until you reach the main roundabout outside Thame (by the Esso petrol station), take the fourth exit which goes to the town centre, bearing left at the first mini-roundabout which takes you up North Street, left again at the second mini-roundabout and you are on the Upper High Street. 30 minutes</li><li>from High Wycombe – Leave High Wycombe from the Handy Cross roundabout heading north on the M40, leave at junction 7 taking the A329 to Thame. Join the A418 ring road to the main roundabout outside Thame (by the Esso petrol station), take the fourth exit which goes to the town centre, bearing left at the first mini-roundabout which takes you up North Street, left again at the second mini-roundabout and you are on the Upper High Street. 40 minutes</li></ul><p>* We are not responsible and accept no liability for any changes in parking regulations – you are advised to check the by-laws yourself.</p><p class="top"><a href="#" title="Top of the page"><svg class="icon icon-arrow-up2"><use xlink:href="#icon-arrow-up2"></use></svg><span>Top</span></a></p></div><!-- .main end --></main> <?php include("inc/footer.php"); ?> <script src="https://widgets.healcode.com/javascripts/healcode.js" type="text/javascript"></script></body></html>